comments: Siakam (IND) moves alongside Holiday's (BOS) path and absorbs the marginal body contact as they come together at the end of the drive.
Toppin (IND) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Siakam (IND) briefly grasps Horford's (BOS) shorts during rebounding.
Brown (BOS) brings his forearm towards Nembhard's (IND) path, and the contact before Nembhard spins away is marginal.  Tatum (BOS) then cleanly deflects the ball away from Nembhard.
Brown (BOS) briefly grasps Nesmith's (IND) arm at the start of his drive.
Nesmith (IND) is moving alongside Brown's (BOS) path and absorbs the marginal contact as he defends the driving shot attempt.
McConnell (IND) steps towards Holiday (BOS), and the contact as they move up the court in transition is marginal.
Siakam (IND) establishes himself in White's (BOS) path and absorbs the marginal contact during the pick.
Brown (BOS) jumps alongside Nembhard's (IND) path and cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
After absorbing the initial contact, Holiday (BOS) briefly grasps Nembhard's (IND) left arm as they disengage following the pick.
Turner's (IND) hand brushes Brown's (BOS) leg and marginal contact occurs as Brown stops to change direction on the perimeter.
Brown (BOS) briefly grasps Siakam's (IND) jersey off ball.
Brown (BOS) legally contests Nembhard's (IND) jump shot attempt.

Turner (IND) grazes Tatum's (BOS) face/head as Tatum secures the rebound, and the contact is marginal.  Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Nesmith (IND) initiates contact with Tatum's (BOS) arm and affects Tatum's SQBR.
Tatum (BOS) is bracing for the contact from Turner (IND) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from Turner.
After releasing the jump shot attempt, Tatum's (BOS) right leg extends slightly and the contact with Turner's (IND) leg and foot is marginal.
Nesmith (IND) makes clean contact with the ball as he attempts to dislodge it away from Holiday (BOS) during the rebound.
Nembhard (IND) attempts to commit a take foul on Holiday (BOS), but the contact is marginal.
